Class ReportXMLReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.reporting.rio.fop.tools.AbstractObjectReader
      • org.kepler.reporting.rio.fop.ReportXMLReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.XMLReader

    public class ReportXMLReader
extends AbstractObjectReader
    XMLReader implementation for the Report class. This class is used to generate SAX events from the Report class.
